msgctxt "#31525"
msgid "Re-run skin shortcuts migrator"
msgstr "Ponovo pokreni migrator prečica maske"

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31526"
msgid "This will rewrite the skin shortcuts .properties file to the current 3 module addon structure. Only run if there are issues with background images or playlists are not working."
msgstr "Ovo će ponovo upisati datoteku .properties prečica maske u trenutnu strukturu dodatka sa 3 modula. Pokrenite ovo samo ako postoje problemi sa pozadinskim slikama ili ako plejliste ne rade."

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31527"
msgid "This will reactivate the addons installer. Only run if addons were not installed when skin was first installed."
msgstr "Ovo će ponovo aktivirati instalaciju dodataka. Pokrenite samo ako dodaci nisu instalirani kada je maska prvi put instalirana."

